ty in 1973 events & presentations chatham house national oil companies and the future of the oil and gas industry december 12 2011 special event mark c thurber peter a nolan paul stevens search people everything recent commentary nolan and thurber identify risk as a major driver of whether countries use private or state owned oil companies december 13 2010 news external presentations chatham house national oil companies and the future of the oil and gas industry mark c thurber peter a nolan paul stevens support map & directions contact rss+ rss xml feeds freeman spogli institute for international studies encina hall 616 serra st stanford ca 94305 6055 tel 650 724 1714 fax 650 725 2592 mail code 6055
